{
  "texts": [
    "This phase involves automating the deployment process to ensure consistency and reliability [93].Operation and Monitoring.",
    "In the \"Operation and Monitoring\" step of DevOps, the focus shifts to maintaining and monitoring the deployed software to ensure optimal performance and security.",
    "This phase involves leveraging actionable intelligence and employing data-driven, eventdriven processes to promptly identify, evaluate, and respond to potential risks [146].",
    "Log analysis is commonly used to detect and diagnose abnormal behavior, enhancing system reliability using data from application logs and runtime environments [22].",
    "Additionally, anomaly detection involves identifying uncommon and unexpected occurrences over time [16]."
  ]
}